        "mainSteps": [ "1. Fetches a list of potentially malicious IP addresses", "2. Sends the list of all malicious IP address to SOC via adaptive card.", "3. Soc can block or ignore unblocked IP address as well as unblock or ignore blocked IP address. " ],
